{"tid":1696741,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"籌備三罷的小開始，今晚開始一齊叫人準備三罷","createTime":"2019-11-06T10:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T11:07:36.000Z","uid":229351,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"214617952ab75e13938b607a216e5c3125521788","tid":1696741,"uid":229351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T10:51:20.000Z","msg":"其實去到第五個月 <br />\n大家應該都明香港人唔會前一日有手足出事，第二日就下到決心罷工<br />\n咁轉變策略一齊慢慢醞釀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好執著要即時三罷<br />\n而是搵一日開始大家一齊無限期三罷<br />\n唔知有竟多人肯無限期三罷，但如果唔係無限期三罷其實無咩意思（罷工一日同平時放一日紅日假無咩分別？<br />\n我覺得真係要日日塞鐵，由某日開始無限期罷<br />\n我是一個好堅持自己gpa要靚靚仔仔的暴大人，但我願意gpa爛到痴線咁每日罷課塞鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知有咩做的人！由今日開始，每日同朋友講無限期罷三！今晚十點開始，大叫「三罷！罷工罷課罷市」！打輿論戰，連儂牆痴文宣！<br />\n香港人！三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！<br />\n手足不是condom！"},{"pid":"88a910e76d608b151c59ae40a65fed2d0b0ec86e","tid":1696741,"uid":229351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T10:52:56.000Z","msg":"自推籌備無限期三罷（1/10）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808b2dc8389454986fb229d80f01ae27db8b7666","tid":1696741,"uid":50414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T10:53:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8641e65f519016ee21828f2f30c1604a3ad05d52","tid":1696741,"uid":229351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T10:53:23.000Z","msg":"自推籌備無限期三罷（2/10）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac